      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCE TOMMY (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 24.63. Jumping from the pinch draw but goes well over this trip. Won at his only start from this box. Great chance to get the job done again. FANCY LENA (1) was a last-start winner from box one at this track over 350m (19.80) after missing the jump, scoring by 3.5 lengths. Has an excellent record from this draw including three wins. Hard to beat again here. LORD EDDIE (5) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (25.01) at this track in a Grade 5 over 440m. Can feature again. CAWBOURNE DOLLAR (8) should be thereabouts.",
